multimedia/headphones includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/headphones

TO START HEADPHONES ON BOOT:
echo 'headphones_enable="YES"' >> /etc/rc.conf

START MANUALLY:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/headphones start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:8181/

